data.description:
Situated along North Ocean Drive in the vibrant community of Hollywood Beach, Costa Hollywood Beach Resort puts travelers in the heart of the action. Steps from the famed Hollywood Beach “Broad Walk” and the beach, guests can enjoy exciting activities like jet skiing, fishing, boating, biking, golfing, and more. Whether your goal is to get the perfect sun tan, catch the big one, or shop the day away, it’s all possible at Hollywood Beach.

Costa Hollywood Beach resort is a vibrant fusion of chic style, warm service, and unique experiences providing an escape designed for spirited adventure and oceanfront relaxation.  Offering rooms and suites featuring an elevated design aesthetic, and luxe décor including high-end Smeg appliances, handmade Italian cabinetry, floor-to-ceiling windows, private patios, and minimalist furnishings.
